description: Mojo Tago is inspired by a love of fresh Mexican cuisine and the LA food truck movement (not to mention a down commercial real estate market).  It’s about good food taGo.  It’s about fun.  It’s about finding your MOJO and you can’t do that on an empty stomach.Mojo Tago is bringing fresh Mex flavors to the people, wherever you may be.  And we’ll find you.  Be on the look out.  We are coming to a street, office building, party, sporting event, community function, festival or something near you!Brian ReedFounder and Manager of the MOJO
name: Mojo Tago
